songs.title: Pour Me (Live at the Hollywood Bowl)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Poor me, floatin' out to sea
An opportunity that went by

Poor you, now what you gonna do?
Now what you gonna do? You just cry

[Verse 2]
Poor me, so blind I couldn't see
The forest for the trees, I don't know why

Poor you, you split yourself in two
Now what you gonna do? You just cry

[Chorus]
I hear you come nearer
I hear you but I don't understand
I hear you come nearer
I hear you but I don't understand

[Verse 3]
Poor me, floatin' out to sea
An opportunity that went by

Poor you, now what you gonna do?
What you gonna do? You just cry

[Chorus]
I hear you come nearer
I hear you but I don't understand
I hear you come nearer
I hear you but I don't understand

[Bridge]
I don't understand
I don't understand
Woooh...

???, I'm gonna feel it now
I'm gonna feel it now
